column1: Dive into a world of seamless interactivity and robust health tracking with our advanced Cosmic Smartwatch. Equipped with a 2.01-inch AMOLED display, this device ensures superior clarity and vibrant visuals. Stay health-conscious with continuous monitoring of heart rate, blood pressure, SpO2 levels, and stress, while the sleep tracker and sedentary reminder keep your wellbeing in check.
• Extensive Fitness Tracking: With over 100 sports modes, step, calorie, and distance tracking, tailor your workout to your personal fitness goals.
• Smart Connectivity: Manage calls, messages, and social media notifications directly from your wrist. Bluetooth 5.1 ensures stable and quick pairing.
• Enhanced Lifestyle Features: Use voice commands with the built-in voice assistant, control your music, and capture moments with remote control photography.
• Durable and Stylish: Comes with two straps to match your style, IP68 water resistance for all-weather wear, and a range of dials to customize your look.
• Extended Battery Life: Enjoy 2-5 days of battery life, keeping you connected without constant charging.

Experience audio excellence with our Hawk Earbuds, designed for crystal-clear sound and uninterrupted focus. Active Noise Cancellation and Dual Mic with ENC (Environmental Noise Cancellation) allow you to enjoy your music or take calls without any distractions.
• Superior Sound Quality: Immerse yourself in rich, detailed sound for up to 4 hours of music playtime and 5 hours of talk time on a single charge.
• Intuitive Controls and Feedback: Manage your listening experience with touch controls and stay informed with the LED battery display.
• Compact and Powerful: The earbuds come with a 35mAH battery, complemented by a 350mAH charging case for extended usage and convenience.

• Ergonomic Design: Designed for comfort and stability, ensuring they stay secure during active use or casual listening.

boost-bundle-1,Boost Bundle 1 : Falcon and Astro,"
Unleash Your Potential with Seamless Connectivity and Health Monitoring

Experience cutting-edge audio technology with the Falcon Earbuds, designed for crystal-clear sound quality and effortless wireless connectivity. These stylish earbuds come in a vibrant yellow silicone shell, offering both comfort and durability. With Bluetooth 5.3 for stable and quick pairing, enjoy music and calls on the go without any hassle. Each earbud is equipped with a 35mAH battery, while the charging case holds 300mAH, supporting wireless charging for maximum convenience. Navigate your audio seamlessly with intuitive touch controls and enjoy the ease of pop-up pairing that connects instantly to your device.

Elevate your wellness journey with the Astro Smart Watch, your all-in-one health and fitness companion. This advanced watch keeps you in tune with your body by monitoring heart rate, blood pressure, blood sugar, blood oxygen, and body temperature. Stay on top of your fitness goals with over 100 sports modes, a sleep tracker, calorie and distance counter, and much more. The AMOLED display brings stunning clarity with an always-on option, housed in a sleek case with two interchangeable straps to suit your style. From receiving calls and social media notifications to remote control photography and Bluetooth calling, the Astro keeps you connected and in control.

The Falcon Earbuds and Astro Smart Watch are designed to work seamlessly together, enhancing your daily life and health routines. Whether you’re taking calls on the move, controlling music during a workout, or monitoring vital health stats, this bundle covers all bases. IP67 water resistance ensures durability across all activities, making this combo perfect for any lifestyle.
